     Complete the intake form for your purchased option:  Semaglutide Intake Form  or  Tirzepatide Intake Form . 
     Fill out the medical questionnaire (takes about 3–5 minutes). 
     Enter your voucher code (look for redemption code when you hit "view voucher" button — different than Groupon Code, example: VS-13PJ-W19J-F9GC-J1G2 — do not use, will not work) in the Discount Code box and click Apply. 
     Add your shipping address and credit card details for future renewals. 
     After submission, you'll receive confirmation, and if approved, we will write a prescription within approximately 12 hours. 
